<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">1.getDerivedStateFromProps</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 是一个静态方法,</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 是一个和组件自身"不相关"的角色.</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 在这个静态方法中,</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 除了两个默认的位置参数</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> nextProps</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 和</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> currentState</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 以外,</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 你无法访问任何组件上的数据.</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">2.会被频繁地触发</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">无论是组件调用了</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> setState</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">()</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379">,</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 接收的</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> props</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 发生了变化,</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 或是父组件的更新都会导致子组件上的</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> getDerivedStateFromProps被触发.</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">相比起在</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> UNSAFE_componentWillReceiveProps</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">(</span><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">nextProps</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">) </span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379">的函数体中直接比较</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> this.props</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 和</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> nextProps</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 上的字段.</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 你需要"绕一个弯"</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 去比较</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> nextProps</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 和</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> currentState.</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">3.使用的时候必须非常小心</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">由于</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> getDerivedStateFromProps</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 会在</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> setState</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">() </span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379">后被调用,</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 并且它的返回值会被用于更新数据.</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 这意味着你会在</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> setState</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">() </span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379">之后触发</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> getDerivedStateFromProps,</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 然后可能意外地再次</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> "setState()".</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
